<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="deny-vt">deny <strong><em>vt</em></strong></h1>
<p>英 /dɪ'naɪ/    美 /dɪ'naɪ/  </p>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1">1.★ <strong>否认；否定：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>He denied all charges. 
他否认所有指控。</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p><strong>There is no denying that</strong> protecting the environment is of great importance. 
不可否认保护环境十分重要。</p></div>

<ul>
<li>deny doing sth：</li>
</ul>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>He denied taking money but we were sceptical. 
他否认收受了贿赂，但我们很怀疑。</p><footer>人教⑤ – 4</footer></div>

<ul>
<li>deny + that 从句：</li>
</ul>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>I never deny that you're a good actor.
我从不否认你是位好演员。</p></div>

<h4 id="2">2.★ <strong>拒绝承认；拒绝接受；拒绝给予：</strong></h4>
<ul>
<li>deny sb sth / deny sth to sb:</li>
</ul>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>No one should be denied a good education. / A good education should be denied to no one.
任何人都不能被剥夺接受良好教育的权利。</p></div>

<h2 id="_2">真题解析</h2>
<ol>
<li>— Are you still mad at her?
— Not really, but I can’t <strong><em>_</em></strong>_ (否认) that her remarks hurt me.   （2011 江苏）<br />
A.deny<br />
B.refuse<br />
C.reject<br />
D.decline  </li>
</ol>
<p>答案：
1. deny  </p></div>